Élizabeth Bourgine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89lizabeth_Bourgine 0 Élizabeth Clémentine Madeleine Bourgine (born 20 March 1957 in Levallois-Perret in the Hauts-de-Seine) is a French actress, appearing in film, television and theater. She is credited with more than 60 roles in film and television, mostly French productions.
